{"tid":457841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子順利邨墮樓亡 丈夫哀傷哭叫亡妻","createTime":"2017-11-04T09:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T09:25:37.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3978d661a3cd6bff542b7e9f11b6d776124ec157","tid":457841,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"下午1時半，秀茂坪順利邨一名年約50歲女子被發現疑由高處墮下，倒卧利逸樓3樓平台，救援人員到場證實她已死亡，警方展開調查，並在利逸樓11樓欄河找到一對相信是死者遺下的膠鞋。死者丈夫到場了解事件，獲悉妻子死訊情緖激動哭喊：「有咩事打畀我先吖嘛！」場面令人心酸。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171104/57417122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171104%2F57417122&d=gYuG1EsZJ%2F3sPoSh6ac4jP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=de79cd2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171104%2F57417122&h=42b1c3bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171104/57417122</a>"},{"pid":"15fe60541a288873cef50212dd50ec817a04b451","tid":457841,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f5df8c6849a91c119d8029fc47a71c8aff9c35","tid":457841,"uid":125237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:23:16.000Z","msg":"順利跳樓"},{"pid":"f8d8193a04cc9edf6e3e61ecf3009792aaae2b38","tid":457841,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"順利墜樓"},{"pid":"8814e29abf82933b38b5c737c558c6333932c93b","tid":457841,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"利溢樓?"